==Open Guide to Boston==

URL = http://boston.openguides.org/

This is a city project participating in the [[Open Guides]] initiative.

This is a contributor-based wiki geared towards describing things and places to do and go in and around Boston. The Guide includes details on as many places as possible within the Boston Metro area, stretching out to the I-495 belt. From Salem to Mattapan, from Wellesley to Eastie, the Open Guide to Boston covers it.


